23.70	Surprised_by_Joy	Surprised by Joy	Surprised by Joy: The Shape of My Early Life is a partial autobiography published by C. S. Lewis in 1955. Specifically the book describes the author's conversion to Christianity which had taken place 24 years earlier.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/74/Surprised_By_Joy_C.S._Lewis_First_Edition.jpg/200px-Surprised_By_Joy_C.S._Lewis_First_Edition.jpg
